						               													<description>Tr&amp;eacute;zors is a luck based card game for 2-4 players. Each player starts with an identical hand of cards, playing through them over the course of the game. A row of treasures is revealed and all players play a card out of their hand simultaneously claiming a type of treasure. If only one player claims a type of treasure in the row, they win that treasure. If more than one player claim the same treasure the first to tap it with their finger wins it. Unclaimed treasures are discarded.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is over when there are no more &amp;quot;chest&amp;rdquo; cards. The players count the number of stars present on the cards won (with rarer treasures being worth more points) and, if needed, subtract a point per &amp;quot;hook&amp;quot; card drawn. The one with the most value points wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents: 59 cards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
